            <div class="footer-dark" style="display:none;"><span>· ─────── ⚜ ─────── ·</span><p class="footer-text">𝕾𝖎𝖑𝖊𝖓𝖙 𝕾𝖈𝖗𝖎𝖕𝖙𝖔𝖗𝖎𝖚𝖒</p></div>
